Why This Matters (The "Business" Impact)
For a non-profit or government agency, this data indicates:

Success Verification: The Veteran data serves as a "Proof of Concept" that dedicated funding works.

Risk Early-Warning: The rising trend in children/family homelessness in 2022 signals a need for immediate resource reallocation toward family-sized emergency shelters.
